      "body" : "```suggestion\r\n        LogPrint(BCLog::NET, \"HEADER ERROR - INVALID MSGTYPE (%s, %u bytes), peer=%d\\n\",\r\n```\r\n\r\nstyle-nit: When changing the log message, might as well change command->msg type, which is preferred in new code.",
